---
title: Crispy Chicken Milanese with Burrata plus Burst Tomato Sauce & Lemony Arugula Salad
description: This fresh spin on chicken Milanese pairs crispy fried chicken cutlets with a bright arugula salad topped with tangy pickled shallot. On the side is a rich burst grape tomato sauce topped with creamy burrata cheese. Get ready for a harmonious blend of textures and flavors for a restaurant-worthy meal to remember!
